 Syntax:  .gripe
          .gripe <last # of messages>
          .gripe <message>

Results:  Allows you to write a gripe/problem to senior wizzes, gods, 
          and admins. Please use where appropriate only.
          Only gods and higher can read these. If they specify a number
          after the command, they can read the specified # of messages
          from the bottom of the baord.
